Section: libs
Priority: required
Depends: libcomposefs, {{ DEPS }}
Description: content-addressed object store for bootable OS trees
 OSTree versions and deploys Linux operating system trees using a
 Git-like content-addressed object model. Deployments are atomic,
 diff-based and fully rollback-capable. It manages /usr and /etc
 while leaving /var and /home as normal mutable storage.
 .
 This build is compiled from upstream sources with composefs integrity
 protection, dracut integration (50ostree initramfs module), the
 ostree-system-generator for early boot, and the prepare-root helper
 required by bootc image deployments.
